*Your Time, Your Rules!*




We=E2=80=99re leveling up our routing engine! We know that in the world of
logistics, every second counts=E2=80=94and more importantly, that no two st=
ops are
the same.


Up until now, our system treated every pickup and delivery with a "one size
fits all" approach to waiting times.


Now we are moving away from defaults to *dynamic, client-defined waiting
times.* You can now explicitly communicate the expected pickup and delivery
duration for every single order at the time of creation.


Why you will love it!

   -

   *No More Underestimating:* Your riders get realistic schedules they can
   actually meet.
   -

   *Zero Guesswork:* Move away from "uniform" timing and embrace the
   variability of your unique operations.

[image: image placeholder]



*What=E2=80=99s new?*

   -

   *Dynamic Wait Times:* You can now pass specific values for every
   individual order at the moment of creation.
   -

   *Hyper-Accurate Route ETAs:* Our routing engine now consumes your custom
   data to calculate total route durations that actually match the real wor=
ld.
   -

   *Total Operational Control:* Whether it=E2=80=99s a complex reverse pick=
up or a
   high-volume consolidation, the system now adapts to your specific busine=
ss
   logic instead of forcing you to adapt to ours.



New parameters =E2=80=9Cpickup_waiting_time =E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Cdelivery=
_waiting_time =E2=80=9D have
been introduced in the API to support this.
